# Deployment Checklist

## Pre-Deployment Validation

- [ ] All tests pass (`python test_complete_ha_bridge.py full`)
- [ ] Documentation updated and accurate
- [ ] Performance validated (response time <2s)
- [ ] Security review completed
- [ ] UI functionality verified
- [ ] Logs reviewed for errors
- [ ] Environment variables configured
- [ ] Dependencies installed and verified

## Production Deployment

- [ ] Follow `docs/DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md` procedures
- [ ] Use Docker for containerized deployment
- [ ] Configure environment variables properly
- [ ] Implement health checks and monitoring
- [ ] Set up log aggregation
- [ ] Configure alerting for critical issues

## Post-Deployment Validation

- [ ] Service health check passes
- [ ] Metrics dashboard functional
- [ ] API endpoints responding correctly
- [ ] Performance within targets
- [ ] No critical errors in logs
- [ ] Monitoring and alerting active

## Environment Configuration

- [ ] Copy `env.example` to `.env` for configuration
- [ ] Set appropriate values for production
- [ ] Secure sensitive configuration data
- [ ] Validate configuration before deployment

## Monitoring Setup

- [ ] Enable Prometheus metrics collection
- [ ] Configure log aggregation
- [ ] Implement health check endpoints
- [ ] Setup alerting for critical issues

